[I] Multipurpose sniffer/interceptor/logger

[T] ettercap is a multipurpose sniffer for switched LANs. It supports
[T] active and passive dissection of many protocols and includes many
[T] features for network and host analysis.

[U] https://www.ettercap-project.org/

